import React from 'react'
import BigDisplay from '../components/BigDisplay'
import Content from '../components/Content'
import TextField from '../components/TextField'
import Button from '../components/Button'

import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row'
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col'

export default () =>
    <>
        <BigDisplay className="bg-white"
            title="Summary"
            subTitle="Please check your details below before submitting."
        />
        
        <Content className="bg-pink">
            <TextField label="Brand Name/ DBA" />
            <TextField label="Online Store Website" />
            <TextField label="Business Owner Email" />
            <TextField label="Federal Tax Classification" />
            <TextField label="Tax Identification Number" />
        </Content>

        <Content className="bg-green">
            <TextField label="Legal Name of the Company" />
            <TextField label="Street Number and Steet Name" />
            <TextField label="Postal Code" />
            <TextField label="City" />
            <TextField label="Country" />
            <TextField label="Province of Incorporation" />
        </Content>


    </>
